 GB\', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">▼</p><p><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56e7f7d363747.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px;\"></p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">虽然已经取得了很高的成</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">但是Easton没有停下前进的脚步</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">在第四版的产品中</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, STHeiti; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;\">Easton提出要用脑电波控制手臂</p><p class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 微软雅黑, MicrosoftYaHei, 宋体, 宋体, Tahoma, Ari