rande\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, \'Open Sans\';\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\">3月15日下午，&ldquo;李世石-Alpha GO人机对战&rdquo;第五局比赛终于收枰，李世石执黑弈至第280手中盘不敌Alpha GO，五盘棋比分打成了1胜4负。Alpha Go是由英国人工智能科技公司 Google DeepMind研发的，公司在2010年建立，前年被谷歌收购。Alpha Go在以其令人惊诧的成绩震撼世人的同时，也让世界看到了人工智能所蕴含的巨大潜力。</span></p><p style=\"font-family: \'Myriad Set Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB W3\', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Lucida Grande\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, \'Open Sans\';\"><br></p><p style=\"font-family: \'Myriad Set Pro\', \'Hiragino Sans GB W3\', å¾®è½¯é›…é»‘â€˜, YaHei, \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Lucida Grande\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, SHSCN, \'Open Sans\'; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;1、为什么是围棋？</span></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;人工智能对于棋类游戏的挑战由来已久。当&ldquo;深蓝&rdquo;在国际象棋上获得成功之后，解决围棋的AI问题就成为了人工智能研究领域最为重大的挑战。围棋是完全信息博弈游戏（perfect information games）之王，它每一步的可能性都远远复杂于国际象棋。一盘150回合的围棋比赛，可能出现的局面达到了惊人的10^171种，对于任何一台人工智能而言，这个数字都基本上等同于无穷，人工智能根本不可能在三个小时的时间里完全枚举出每一次落子的可能情况并对此做出计算。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;那么Alpha Go到底是如何下围棋的呢？感兴趣的童鞋不防研究一下下面这张图，据说是目前对AlphaGo原理最清晰简明的中文解析~（图片版权属于作者 郑宇，张钧波）</section></section></section></section><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ec1162c0911.jpeg\" style=\"width: 465px;\"></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、人工智能威胁论？</span></div><div data-empty=\"true\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ec11947ee76.jpeg\" style=\"width: 461px;\"></span><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;人工智能的领域十分广泛，从无人驾驶汽车与你对话的Siri都可以被称之为人工智能。但正如计算机科学家Donald Knuth说，&ldquo;人工智能已经在几乎所有需要思考的领域超过了人类，但是在那些人类和其它动物不需要思考就能完成的事情上，还差得很远。&rdquo;</section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.78;\">弱人工智能Artificial Narrow Intelligence (ANI): 弱人工智能是擅长于单个方面的人工智能。比如有能战胜象棋世界冠军的人工智能，但是它只会下象棋，你要问它怎样更好地在硬盘上储存数据，它就不知道怎么回答你了。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">强人工智能Artificial General Intelligence (AGI)：强人工智能要求程序有自己的思维，能够理解外部事物并自发做出决策甚至行动，其表现就像一个&ldquo;人&rdquo;一样，甚至很可能比人的反应更杰出、更可靠。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">超人工智能Artificial Superintelligence (ASI): 牛津哲学家，知名人工智能思想家Nick Bostrom把超级智能定义为&ldquo;在几乎所有领域都比最聪明的人类大脑都聪明很多，包括科学创新、通识和社交技能。&rdquo;</section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;简单来说，我们目前能做到的人工智能都是弱人工智能，所谓人工智能的&ldquo;威胁&rdquo;都至少来自强人工智能，而强人工智能至今仍只是一个&ldquo;假说&rdquo;。所谓的比尔盖茨对此的担忧也只是出于对强人工智能的警惕，这丝毫不影响我们对于弱人工智能的开发与利用。</section></section></section></section></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">3、Alpha Go的未来？</span></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section></section></section></section></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; DeepMind联合创始人兼CEO杰米斯&middot;哈萨比斯认为AI未来的应用领域将会集中在医疗保健、智能手机助手以及机器人学等方面。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; 以下是The Verge对他的采访部分摘录：</section></section></section></section><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ec12318f711.jpeg\" style=\"width: 474px;\"><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; border: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border-top-left-radius: 100%; border-top-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-left-radius: 100%; text-align: center; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Alpha Go与游戏</strong></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Q:如果让你把现在人工智能的成果带回游戏领域会如何呢？看起来这件事情是顺理成章的。</strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A:嗯，我觉得这会很棒。事实上，我这两天跟几家大游戏公司，譬如说EA之类的&hellip;&hellip;有过联系。我们应该会把这个成果引入游戏界，运用这些最新的成果可以让游戏AI的水平突飞猛进，因为客观需求摆在这里嘛。不过目前我们更愿意把精力放在健康服务或是人事推荐系统这样更加现实的事情上。游戏业界当然是个很重要的市场，把我们的AI系统推向游戏业界前途广阔，而我觉得开发者们也会更乐于使用成熟的学习型AI（而不是自己开发），或许不久的将来，开发者们只需要对AI进行微调就可以了。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Q:我刚刚正好想到你是不是在家里打游戏的时候，被糟糕的AI气到过。</strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A:哈哈哈，是的。一些大型多人在线游戏就经常让我恼火。这些游戏里面的AI都很蠢，他们没有记忆，也不会根据玩家的行动做出改变，行为更不会进化。如果我们把学习型AI放到这些游戏里面，整个游戏的可玩度肯定会大大提高。</section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; border: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border-top-left-radius: 100%; border-top-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-left-radius: 100%; text-align: center; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Alpha Go与智能手机助手</strong></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Q:我在开幕日上看到你在演讲时使用了一张电影《她》（斯派克&middot;琼斯2013年拍摄的科幻电影）的海报，这是不是人工智能的终极形态呢？</strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A:并非如此。但《她》这样的电影是让公众理解人工智能的最好方式。我想做的是让智能手机助手变得真正&ldquo;智能&rdquo;，有条理，并且能够真正理解用户究竟想做什么。目前，大多数这样的系统并不好用，一旦你的问题超出了他们的模板，他们就不能给你有用的回复。因此，我们要做的是让这些手机助手更加适用、灵活、强大。</section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ec125457656.jpeg\" style=\"width: 453px;\"><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Q:对于这些领域，你们需要一些怎样的突破呢？为什么我们不能立刻着手呢？</strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A:事实上我们确实已经可以实现一些构想了，但是达到这些目标需要不同的途径。在设定回应模板与机械学习之间有着巨大的鸿沟。现在的智能手机基本上是通过设定回应模板的方式来达成手机助手的功能的，因此他们的稳定性并不是很好，只能通过模板完成工作。然而真实世界要远远比模板复杂得多，你不可能在模板中把所有的用户行为都预料到。我们建立DeepMind的原则就是从原则和基础之上进行学习。</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Q:你认为这些研究成果什么时候能够呈现在智能手机上并被大众所用呢？</strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A:我觉得，在接下来的<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">两到三年</strong>里你就可以看到这些成果的开始应用，并且对工作与生活有切实的影响。而在五六年之后，你就会发现这些技术对生活的巨大改变了。</section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; border: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border-top-left-radius: 100%; border-top-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-left-radius: 100%; text-align: center; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Alpha Go与科学研究</strong></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Q:你对未来人类、机器人以及AI之间的互动、关联有些什么想法呢？显而易见人们都向往美丽神奇的科幻世界。</strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A:我个人对于机器人领域并没有太多的关注。我更关心的是这些AI能对科学的进步有多少助益，以及他们的发展能有多快。我希望AI能够代替人类处理一些艰苦却琐碎的工作，比如说检索相关的文章，从大量数据中总结出他们的结构，这样一来人类的科学突破会有着更大的突破。几个月前我曾经与欧洲核子研究组织（European Organization for Nuclear Research，简称CERN）的人进行过交流，他们有着世界上最为庞大的数据量，在那些浩如烟海的硬盘中很有可能存在着新粒子的数据，但由于数据量太多，他们还尚未被发现。所以有时候我会想某天AI能够帮助人类找到一些全新的粒子，这种事情一定非常酷。</section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></div>','2016-03-18 22:44:05',39,'13634129020',4,4,0,'56ec1435918d1.jpeg','56ec1435918d1_thumb.jpeg'),(63,'他说我要把你娶回家——”四爷“”若曦“今日完婚','一个吻，一句“我愿意”，成就了他们的幸福。','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">盼望着，盼望着，我们的女神终于穿上一身白婚纱，踏进了婚礼的殿堂。<img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9dc5573fa.jpg\" style=\"width: 362px;\"><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee99082d5d5.jpg\" style=\"width: 359px;\"></p><p><br></p><hr><p><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2<span>013年11月13日凌晨，吴奇隆在微博上首先发布消息承认与刘诗诗的恋情，并称我們很珍惜这份得之不易的感情，并请求外界给予自由的时间与空间。（吴奇隆微博原文：&ldquo;谢谢大家的关心及祝福，我们很珍惜这份得之不易的感情，真心的希望大家在我们仅有的私人生活里，给予一些自由的时间与空间，谢谢体谅。&rdquo;）</span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span><span><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9a5423596.jpeg\" style=\"width: 465px;\"></span></span><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9a6df2cae.jpg\" style=\"width: 451px;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一部虐恋穿越剧《步步惊心》，让&ldquo;四爷&rdquo;吴奇隆和&ldquo;若曦&rdquo;刘诗诗的人气大增。两人的戏中演绎的缠绵悱恻的动人爱情不知道俘获了多少观众的眼泪。虽然剧中的两人最终没能相依相守，但却丝毫不影响两人成为了年度最登对情侣。</span></p><p><span><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9b8fd40c2.jpg\" style=\"width: 370px;\"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;继《步步惊心》之后，他们再度合作《步步惊情》，诗诗饰演<span>张晓、蓝兰，吴奇隆饰演<span>殷正。</span></span>这让不少隆诗cp粉兴奋不已，每天守着电视看这部剧。</p><p><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9c16e95da.jpg\" style=\"width: 348px;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 吴奇隆刘诗诗在<span>继《步步惊心》、《步步惊情》之后刘诗诗与吴奇隆三度合作，投入拍摄古装轻喜剧《犀利仁师》，他们在这部剧中又分别担任男女主角&ldquo;<span>柳傲天&rdquo;和&ldquo;<span>路云霏&rdquo;</span></span>，上演一对欢喜冤家麻辣老师。</span></span></p><p><span><span><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9d63a8e9a.jpg\" style=\"width: 450px;\"></span></span><img class=\"fr-dib fr-img-move\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9d7de4194.jpg\" style=\"width: 361px;\"><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9d92b249d.png\" style=\"width: 413px;\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2015年1月20日中午，吴奇隆在微博宣布与刘诗诗领证结婚。他发微博称＂珍惜幸福＂，并附上结婚证与钻戒的照片。刘诗诗随后转发该微博，称＂我们很幸福＂。消息一出，立刻引发广大网友热议，<span>消息一出引得网友广发热议，网友纷纷送上祝福，直呼&ldquo;若曦和四爷终于完满啦。&rdquo;</span></span></p><hr><p><span><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9e276d8a9.jpg\" style=\"width: 354px;\"></span><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56ee9e3a6c418.png\" style=\"width: 439px;\"></p><p><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea2ae014ec.JPG\" style=\"width: 373px;\"><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 如今，四爷和若曦终于携手，他们一路走来，平淡而幸福，让人倍感温馨。他们收获的不光是在场圈内好友及亲戚的祝福，还有我们这些在电脑手机屏幕前一遍一遍观看他们婚礼现场的观众们的祝福。</p><p><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea1c000f53.jpg\" style=\"width: 395px;\"><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在婚礼上，吴奇隆含泪表白：&ldquo;我也不止一次的埋怨过老天，以前我老埋怨老天对我不公平，让我经历一些磨难、不开心的事情，现在我终于知道了，我也明白了为什么，因为它把最好的留给我了，我会听话的。&rdquo;</p><p><img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea07583abd.jpg\" style=\"width: 485px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&rdquo;我一定会把你娶回来&ldquo;&mdash;&mdash;这是最完美的结局。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">祝福他们，白头偕老，永远幸福。</p>','2016-05-20 21:30:41',46,'15967146881',3,3,0,'56eea601351af.jpg','56eea601351af_thumb.jpg'),(64,'那时，我怎么会喜欢你','年少时，我们说不清道不明的爱情。','<p><strong>我们能不能不分手</strong><a class=\"audio_start\" href=\"javascript%3Avoid(0)\"></a></p><div class=\"audio\"><a class=\"audio_start\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\"><span class=\"tit\">我们能不能不分手</span><b class=\"audio-play audio_icon\">&nbsp;</b><span class=\"tit f-r\">3:34</span></a><audio src=\"http://localhost:9096/cl/Data/audio/570b4b98178b1.mp3\" controls=\"controls\" hidden=\"true\">&nbsp;</audio></div><p>喜欢了你三年，不喜欢你也三年了，如今我们各自奔向大学，从朋友那里知道你去了N大学，那是我的第二志愿，差一点，我们又离得很近了。<img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea8bb3c7b0.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px;\"></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 六年前，星期五，阴天，校车上，我第一次见到你，然后一见钟情。我一直以为自己是个只会日久生情的人&hellip;&hellip;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 那天，你穿了一件红色的格子衬衫，我应该永远都不会忘记那件衣服，因为你和我旁边的同学撞衫了，还是个女生，叫WM。我还记得那时候她看到你穿着和她一样的衬衫时尴尬的表情，想说脏话，却欲言又止，然后以迅雷不及掩耳之势脱掉了衬衫，幸好里面还有衣服。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 我一直在旁边憋笑，然后偷偷地打量你。那时你留着板寸头，看上去干净利落，一副很书生的样子，但手里却拿着游戏机玩的认真。一路上大家有说有笑，但我总是斜眼偷看你，而你一直都只是认真地玩游戏。我喜欢做事认真的男生，即便是在玩游戏机。﻿﻿好吧，我承认那时我就对你有了好感。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 后来，我开始四处打听你，但不是明目张胆的方式。某天，你从我身旁走过，我做作地问我同学，&quot;哎，那人是谁啊，走路好奇葩啊？&quot;她一脸不解地回答：&quot;有吗？不是很正常嘛，三班的FY，长得还蛮帅的啊！&quot;我装作很是嫌弃的样子，&quot;不帅！额，你的眼光真是独特！&quot;其实她不知道我的内心是无比赞同她说的话。</p><p>&nbsp; 而后我又用这种战术要到了你的各项信息，当然包括QQ。<img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea8c720238.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px;\"></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;我战战兢兢地加了你为好友，祈祷上帝你千万不要问我是谁，可你还是不出所料地问了，周旋了一会儿后如实回答，然后竟然脑子过热地告白了&hellip;&hellip;说来也真是后悔。当然不用说，结果肯定被拒绝了呗，我尴尬地删了好友，苦恼于以后见面的时候怎么办，我可是把我的信息都告诉你了啊，不过也只好走一步看一步了。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 虽然告白失败了，但是不代表我就不喜欢你了啊。我依旧像个小花痴，默默地追随着你。习惯在拥挤的人群里寻找你的身影，找到了，就有胜过一切的莫名开心，找不到，就有淹没所有开心的莫名伤感。习惯每天四点半风雨球场，你打羽毛球的飒爽英姿；习惯在优秀学员名单上看到你的名字，然后像个胜利者一样骄傲地笑&hellip;&hellip;我也曾像个懵懂的女孩听信那些爱情魔咒，在本子上写了一千遍你的名字，却依旧没有等来你的爱&hellip;&hellip;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;当然我也是听说过一些关于你的&ldquo;事迹&rdquo;，三年下来，你换了好多女朋友，和我第一次见你时的印象不同，原来你也是个花花公子。为你的女朋友做过很浪漫的事，那时，我把自己代入女主，感受你的温柔，梦里都笑得灿烂。也见过你&ldquo;娇羞&rdquo;地追求别人的样子，真希望看到你也对我这样&hellip;&hellip;<img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea8d2802d0.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px;\"></p><p>&nbsp; 毕业季，大家都忙着告白和告别，那个时候我下定决心不再喜欢你，和过去的自己say goodbye。三年的单恋，没有奢望有任何的回报，像个痴人一样默默地守候，默默地等待。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 没有想到在高中又遇见了你，隔壁班，兄弟班，少不了撞见的机会。我发现你的发型变了，酒红色的鸡窝头，个还是没长，表情更丰富了，多了曾经没有的坚定眼神，好像你已经不再是我原来喜欢上你的样子了。每次和你相遇时，我还是会偷偷看你，但已不再是过去那种爱慕的偷看，我只是想看看你是否还记得我曾经脑子过热的告白，你用孤傲的眼神回答yes。而后我便不再愿意和你对视，我也要用我孤傲的表情告诉你，我不喜欢你了。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;你还是一如既往的花花公子，和某人某人谈着恋爱，而我却不会再因此而伤心难过。你说，那时我怎么会喜欢上你呢？好像你都不是我想要的类型，却无法自拔&hellip;&hellip;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;和室友闲聊时，听她提起表弟的暗恋史，四年了，他做了四年的备胎，默默付出，像个傻子一样，说她的一颦一笑就是最值得的回报。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;好像，那个时候的我们都一样，纯洁天真，不会去追究对方的家世背景，不会在意对方没车没房，不会考虑最后你是否会爱我&hellip;&hellip;<img class=\"fr-dib\" src=\"http://www.campusleader.cn/Data/Upload/56eea8f083057.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px;\"></p><p>文／近崖思岸（简书作者）</p><p>原文链接：http://www.jianshu.com/p/c3e4946d92c5</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','2016-05-20 21:43:28',38,'15967146881',5,5,0,'56eea9006f81a.jpg','56eea9006f81a_thumb.jpg'),(67,'dasdas ','fgdsgfdg','<div class=\"audio\"><p class=\"audio_start\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\"><span class=\"tit\">我们能不能不分手</span><span class=\"tit pull-right m-r-sm\">2:52</span></p><audio src=\"http://localhost:9096/cl/Data/audio/5705008cc164c.mp3\" controls=\"controls\" hidden=\"true\">&nbsp;</audio></div><p><br></p>','2016-05-06 20:27:04',4,'2',3,20,0,'57050097d12da.jpg','57050097d12da_thumb.jpg'),(68,'dasdasd ','dasdasd','<div class=\"audio\"><a class=\"audio_start\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\"><span class=\"tit\">我们能不能不分手</span><b class=\"audio-play audio_icon\">&nbsp;</b><span class=\"tit pull-right m-r-sm\">2:52</span></a><audio src=\"http://localhost:9096/cl/Data/audio/57051647f1fd4.mp3\" controls=\"controls\" hidden=\"true\">&nbsp;</audio></div><p><br></p>','2016-05-06 21:59:55',10,'2',1,1,0,'5705165a904c8.jpg','5705165a904c8_thumb.jpg'),(69,'东莞理工学院一女','方式的个的复合弓','<p>近日，东莞理工学院一女生上课看手机，被任课老师要求当场砸碎，&ldquo;不砸你就挂科&rdquo;，该女生只好砸碎手机。校方：做法过于严苛，要求涉事老师赔偿学生手机。有老师称，该老师方式虽会有极端，但对学生负责也有好处。</p><p><span contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"fr-video fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"http://open.iqiyi.com/developer/player_js/coopPlayerIndex.html?vid=c1772eea35a6b3e532866d0b07a6b940&amp;tvId=471686000&amp;accessToken=2.f22860a2479ad60d8da7697274de9346&amp;appKey=3955c3425